sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as LlamaStack Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant LlamaServer as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as Client Pod
    participant ExtClient as External Client
    participant IngressCtrl as OpenShift Router /<br/>Ingress Controller

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 1: CR Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (CR created/updated)<br/>HTTPS/6443 | SA token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment, Service,<br/>PVC, NetworkPolicy, SA, CRB<br/>HTTPS/6443 | SA token
        Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP/8321 | plaintext | no auth
        LlamaServer-->>Operator: 200 OK
        Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321 | plaintext | no auth
        LlamaServer-->>Operator: Provider info JSON
        Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321 | plaintext | no auth
        LlamaServer-->>Operator: Version info
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>HTTPS/6443 | SA token
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,LlamaServer: Flow 2: Internal Access
        Client->>LlamaServer: POST /v1/inference/...<br/>HTTP/8321 | plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy enforced
        LlamaServer-->>Client: Inference Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over ExtClient,LlamaServer: Flow 3: External Access (via Ingress)
        ExtClient->>IngressCtrl: HTTPS/443 or HTTP/80<br/>Depends on ingress config
        IngressCtrl->>LlamaServer: HTTP/8321 | plaintext
        LlamaServer-->>IngressCtrl: Response
        IngressCtrl-->>ExtClient: Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 230)
        Note over K8sAPI,Operator: Flow 4: ConfigMap Rolling Update
        K8sAPI->>Operator: ConfigMap watch event<br/>HTTPS/6443 | SA token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment annotation<br/>(content hash)<br/>HTTPS/6443 | SA token
        Note over K8sAPI: Kubernetes rolls pods<br/>with updated ConfigMap
    end
